Maybe you're busy trying to find a way to recover your files, but don't waste your time. No one can decrypt them. Without the service, the files cannot be recovered.
Can I recover my files? Certainly. You can recover all your files safely and easily, but you don't have enough time for that. You have to pay to decrypt all files. You only have 3 days left to submit your payment. After that, the price will double. Also, if you don't pay within 7 days, you can't permanently recover your files. We'll have a free event for the very poor people who don't pay in 6 months.
